# <type>: <subject>
#
# <body>
#
# <footer>
#
# Type should be one of:
#   feat:     New feature
#   fix:      Bug fix
#   docs:     Documentation changes
#   style:    Code style changes (formatting, etc)
#   refactor: Code refactoring
#   test:     Test changes
#   chore:    Build/tooling changes
#
# Subject should be imperative, present tense, lowercase, no period at end
#
# Body should include motivation for the change and contrast with previous behavior
#
# Footer should reference issues (e.g., "Closes #123") or note breaking changes
# (e.g., "BREAKING CHANGE: API endpoint removed")
